# Build and Start Workflow

After making changes to the Markdown Viewer codebase, remember to build and start the application to see your changes:

1. Accept all changes made during the session
2. Run `npm run build` to build the application
   ```bash
   npm run build
   ```
3. Run `npm run start` to start the application
   ```bash
   npm run start
   ```

## Key Project Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Contains the build and start scripts
- [webpack.config.js](mdc:webpack.config.js) - Build configuration
- [src/App.jsx](mdc:src/App.jsx) - Main application component
- [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global styles
- [src/splitPane.css](mdc:src/splitPane.css) - Split pane styles
- [src/components/MarkdownEditor.jsx](mdc:src/components/MarkdownEditor.jsx) - Editor component
- [src/components/MarkdownPreview.jsx](mdc:src/components/MarkdownPreview.jsx) - Preview component
